</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-1816_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The Mandatory Training Group leverages AR to craft engaging learning experiences that not only draw learners in but also significantly enhance knowledge retention. By turning abstract concepts into tangible, interactive simulations, AR makes learning more intuitive and impactful.
