</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-1820_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">AR technology offers learners the chance to practise and hone skills in a risk-free environment. This is particularly beneficial in fields like healthcare, where The Mandatory Training Group provides AR content that allows for the safe simulation of medical procedures.
